query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math',
'mathoverflow',
'pt',
'serverfault')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ac.commutative-algebra',
'android',
'approximation',
'conditional-expectation',
'contour-integration',
'differential-geometry',
'domain-name-system',
'group-theory',
'harmonic-analysis',
'javascript',
'partial-derivative',
'pde',
'set-theory',
'stochastic-calculus',
'ubuntu')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
